      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PRINCE LEGACY (2) has some solid form under his belt and proved too strong last time to win by 2.5 lengths at this track in a handy 24.77 beating Giggle Hat. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. In sparkling form and looks the one to beat again. BANDIT BLAZE (4) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 3.5 lengths at Temora in a handy 18.68. Has a tricky draw to overcome but goes well over this trip. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Significant danger. HELLO HILDA (3) hit the ground running off the inside draw and there until late when holding on for a minor finishing second (30.33) at Nowra in a Mix over 520m. Was a winner at her only start from this draw. Expecting another good run. DARK SHINE (1) should be in the finish fresh from a 12 weeks break.",
